Interface WithFormFlow<I,O,F>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - type of the input data, possibly a parameter object
    O - type of the output object, normally the updated object if the form is valid
    F - stereotype of the in a form wrapped class
    All Superinterfaces:
    WithForm<F>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    WithTemplateFormFlow<I,O,F>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SunriseAddAddressController, SunriseAddLineItemController, SunriseChangeAddressController, SunriseChangeCountryController, SunriseChangeLanguageController, SunriseChangeLineItemQuantityController, SunriseCheckoutAddressController, SunriseCheckoutConfirmationController, SunriseCheckoutPaymentController, SunriseCheckoutShippingController, SunriseLogInController, SunriseMyPersonalDetailsController, SunriseRemoveAddressController, SunriseRemoveLineItemController, SunriseSignUpController
